  "text": "For each iteration of optimization, we execute the standard Kaldi training recipe upto the speaker dependent training stage (tri4b) for Wall Street Journal [CITATION_1] . We use MFCC features with the window size and window shift as specified by the hyperparameters. Then, alignments from this model along with logMel filter-bank features are used to create the training data for the DNN.",
